Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:35.99,Shadow house-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(397,517)\pos(1442,852.667)}前往與祖父大人共住的樓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,紅茶是非常精緻的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:51.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,注入開水之後  要蓋上蓋子慢慢浸泡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,關鍵是不能急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:57.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,揭開蓋子  用勺子輕輕攪拌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,用漏勺過濾後倒入杯子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:06.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,然後品一下茶香  再嚐一口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這就是大人的喝法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:13.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你口渴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,給你喝加了很多糖的紅茶好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過  你要先回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:27.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你的主人是叛亂分子  沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特究竟在謀劃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我沒有什麼可以說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:39.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒有凱特小姐的許可我是什麼都不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,威…威脅我也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只是一段時間不能喝水而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:57.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要是那個時候把麵包吃完就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是個毫無緊張感的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:06.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,時間還很多  我要在早上之前挖出所有秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:09.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,送到偉大的祖父大人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.84,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,愛德華是在祖父大人那棟對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說我們得潛入那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那種事情真的能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你再稍微認真想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那喬恩你來想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我一下子也想不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:32.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你有什麼主意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:40.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你總是沉著冷靜  會觀察周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可是這麼跟我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請你幫幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:49.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯吧  尚恩確實是很聰明  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我明白了  請給我點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:57.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:02.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣才能不被發現地去到祖父大人那棟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,況且情報也太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:08.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,完全不知道那棟宅邸是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可能還會設有什麼陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:17.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,連通祖父大人那棟的路我就只知道那條走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:21.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可是入口有無面人偶在看守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:23.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:31.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我想到了  唯一一個成功的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:43.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在吃麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是頑強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過你還能靠妄想撐到到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒關係  我已經飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:05:00.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只要你告訴我凱特在謀劃的事情  給你鬆綁也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那就繼續綁著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這我也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:05.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那你就把凱特…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:06.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你知道現在是什麼情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:13.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:18.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,吃飽之後我就犯睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那我們來聊點開心的話題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:25.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,其實你也不樂意做這種事的  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.84,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我不會說有關凱特小姐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是你的事情不管多少我都會聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們來聊各種話題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那樣絕對很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:50.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,別急啊愛德華  這不是什麼難事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:55.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們要從這個走廊堂堂正正地前往對面的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,偽裝成無面人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:03.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,原來如此  愛德華也是這樣過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不愧是尚恩  注意到了關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您過獎了  喬恩少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:12.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那喬恩也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:16.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,人數越多  被發現的風險也越高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可是我們不是不知道埃米莉可在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,分頭去找比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不行  我們沒有互相聯絡的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:31.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過  一個人去那間宅邸找人也太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我在書裡看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:38.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,祖父大人那一棟  樓層越高住的人身份越高貴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有一樓  二樓  三樓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你們覺得愛德華會住在哪一樓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,話說像他那樣的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:49.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要用誘拐這樣鬼鬼祟祟的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,鬼鬼祟祟…確實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.97,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼他要冒這種風險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:07:01.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我說  還要偷無面人偶的制服吧  你打算怎麼偷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對  肯定有個地方放著替換用的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這個時間會是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:14.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克  馬上開門  你在吵什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,芭芭拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那個戴星的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不好了  聲音被聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,從利奇的房間逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:26.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是活人偶的房間在外面上了鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:29.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,一旦有情況就用喬恩拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:32.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不可以  門壞掉的話  帕利克少爺會被懷疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:37.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你打算讓我等到什麼時候  快點開門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒有思考的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:44.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,總之這裡就交給帕利克和利奇吧  大家走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:50.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,利奇  就那樣辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:55.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,芭芭拉  深更半夜的有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:59.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,剛才從這房間裡傳出了好幾個人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,作為戴星組  我要進行室內搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你那是誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:07.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是誤會的話  檢查一下也不會有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,芭比  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不行  鎖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了  把門破壞掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:19.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,等等  我們有麻煩了  過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏絲  你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,巡邏辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在和誰講話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好了  我們逃出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:47.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:53.97,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏絲的黑灰可以控制活人偶啊  你們已經忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這裡沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:02.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,最後只剩活人偶的房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這之後要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,首先要弄到制服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那繼續控制她給我們帶路就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯  凱特和露薏絲一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那喬恩我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:33.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們去看下對面樓那邊的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說不定能發現潛入的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:39.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也對  我們在那個走廊前集合吧  凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了  千萬不要被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:50.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,都怪我一不小心和利奇聊得太熱烈了  我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:52.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那個  你之前有巡邏過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:10:00.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,愛德華成為兒童樓的管理員之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要求我們包括小糾紛在內的所有問題都要報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,愛德華？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他在「露面」中被表揚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:12.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是呢  但事無巨細都要報告嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是因為他很渴望出人頭地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,令人火大的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,芭芭拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:27.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這之後少做些可疑的舉動  帕利克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:28.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:42.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是好險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:46.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,剛才的情報能用來救埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:48.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要為了那樣的活人偶做到這個份上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,才不是「那樣的活人偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她是埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,還有  你是利奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這  肯定會有守衛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,到關鍵時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:17.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不能用喬恩拳  要是他們呼叫救援怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:23.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,仔細一看  離得相當遠啊  懸崖還很高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這麼黑也看不太清
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們去過的就只有「露面」的那一層
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:34.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,現在就只能將看得見的外觀和記憶中的對照起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,想像宅邸的內部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯  很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:48.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那露薏絲就陪你到這了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我不想繼續以身犯險了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,之後你就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.65,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,幫大忙了  真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我只是想炫耀自己的黑灰能力而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這對露薏絲來說是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯  麻煩祝我成功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏絲小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,雖然這次他盯上的碰巧是凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但之後說不定會輪到露薏絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:28.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就是說  他也許會搶走露對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我絕對不會讓他對露出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我最討厭愛德華了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,糟了  被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:43.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,等等  我是凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:47.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:47.70,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們這棟的一樓與對面的地下一層相連對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:57.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,穿過走廊之後  請您去找樓梯往上走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:01.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我猜對面的棟也會有人偶巡邏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但既然扮作「看不見臉的人偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算被發現應該也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是要上到三樓  再怎麼說也有點難了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不  沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克和利奇  你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:20.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,聽芭芭拉說  愛德華是兒童棟的管理人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:23.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他想更出人頭地上到三樓去  也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他住在二樓或一樓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:29.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但房間的數量也很多  不可能一間間去查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,交給凱特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可別失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:41.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:45.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯  一定會兩個人一起回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:51.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因為我很擔心啊  喬恩替你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你幫我到這裡就已經足夠了  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:57.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也謝謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她好像成功進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克我們也該回房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:58.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,被巡邏的發現就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們也回去吧  喬恩少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:07.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這難道是裝咖啡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,看來是在這裡製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,都是正常的瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,果然是在泡完咖啡之後加了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:08.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我這樣做也是為了凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我想在無法挽回之前拯救她  所以需要你幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,再這樣下去凱特會被處置的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:19.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因為你毫無用處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:27.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,正因為有像你這樣的廢物  凱特才不會嚮往高處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:32.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,所以她才會想要背叛影宅  這跟小孩子鬧脾氣是一個道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只是在洩憤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:36.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請不要說凱特小姐的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你心裡沒點數嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:43.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你總是想多餘的事  無視規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:50.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你不覺得是不守影宅規矩的你引導凱特走錯路的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,聽著  現在我給你一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:02.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只要你全都招認  我就會救凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,現在能救凱特的就只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.84,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快說吧  凱特在謀劃著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,大箱子？難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小麵包  在的話就動一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,告訴我你在這
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,再試一次  更用力一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:47.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,黑灰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我要專心尋找埃米莉可才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,麵包？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:12.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:21.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快  回答我  凱特在謀劃著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,比任何人都勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,比任何人都溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她是我最重要的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,地板都被你弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,給我安靜待著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,難道是用來拐走埃米莉可的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:09.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧  我在外面聽到了什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你還真的把她抓來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,去外面說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:32.65,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,剛才應該是小麵包撞倒杯子落地的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:40.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐為了讓我恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哭著讓我喝下了水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:47.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,把我看做一個獨立的人  叫我埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:52.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,總是溫柔地守護著冒失的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:03.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐  凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,很好  沒有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不能慌了神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:36.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我想去確認愛德華說有侵入者的事情是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,想救那個活人偶的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:44.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她就會模仿愛德華變裝成「看不見臉的人偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:48.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,到時候應該會推著推車過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,總不可能把推車搬到二樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只要數一下地下一層的推車數量就知道她有沒有來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:07.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,糟了  得在那兩個人回來之前救出埃米莉可才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小麵包  你在的話就給點反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:19.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,告訴我埃米莉可的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:21.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:26.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:28.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我在這裡  凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:34.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哪裡  你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:42.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:47.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎  我現在幫你解開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們現在快離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不是的  凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:56.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:04.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
